Explanation:

localhost: Refers to your local machine (127.0.0.1).
8080: The port number where Apache Tomcat (the web server) is running.
/student-system: The context path of the web application (defined in pom.xml).
After running the Maven command (mvn clean compile tomcat7:run), the server starts and displays this link in the terminal. Open any web browser and paste this URL to access the Student Information System dashboard.